dct_title_s: Map of the  South Carolina State highway system showing road conditions as of January 1,1933 / drawn by D.R. Baker.
dct_description_sm: Panel title. "Drawn by: D.R. Baker." Map on verso (40 x 52 cm.): Regional map showing principal through routes of the eastern United States. Panel art: state seal.
dct_publisher_sm: Columbia, South Carolina : The State Company, 1933.
